process

void process(String token,
             String separator,
             String separatorPattern)
             throws UtilityException
Processes a token that is found by a splitter.

Parameters:
token - the text before the separator
separator - the separator that was found (the empty string in case of the last token)
separatorPattern - the pattern that matches the separator that was found (null for the last token)
Throws:
UtilityException - when the token can't be processed (e.g. when the separator order is unexpected)
